                    <app><note>Text based on photographs</note></app>
                    <app loc="3"><note>Franz corrected the phonetic spelling in Καλάτυχος, but Korhonen thinks of a stonecutter’s error for Καλλίτυχος (attested also in Sicily: LGPN 3A: 235) </note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><note>Amico, Torremuzza, Franz: ϙ; Ferrara, Kaibel, Korhonen: ο</note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><note>Amico, Torremuzza, Ferrara, Franz: δ; Kaibel, Korhonen: γ</note></app>
                    <app loc="6"><note>ΓΛΜΙΚΗΙΧΝΔΤΙ lapis; Torremuzza: γαμικὴ γιλυκυτάτη; Ferrara; Korhonen: γαμικὴ ἀνδρί; Kaibel: τ(ῷ) ἀνδρί (less probable τἀνδρί) </note></app> 
                </listApp>
